## ğŸ¯ Objective
Set up the **Mythic Command and Control (C2) Server** and understand how it works in a red team or adversary emulation context.



## ğŸ§° Prerequisites
- âœ… A fresh **Ubuntu Server** VM for the Mythic server
- âœ… An **attacker machine** (e.g., Kali Linux or Parrot OS)
